title: Ibb.and.Obb-HI2U
description:
HI2U!

ibb & obb (c) Sparpweed

Release Date : 28th of May, 2014
Protection   : Steam
Type         : Adventure/Action/Indie
Size         : 11 x 50mb

Description:
~~~~~~~~~~~~

ibb & obb is a two player cooperative game set in a puzzle filled world
where gravity goes both up and down. You can only succeed by working
closely together.

Find a friend for some true local co-op couch fun or match up online.

Fall up and jump down through 15 levels filled with double gravity puzzles
and discover 8 hidden worlds that will test your new non-Newtonian skills
to the maximum.

All levels have their own unique music, composed by Kettel, known for his
warm melodic electronica.

Key Features:

* Local and online co-op
* Warm electronic soundtrack by Kettel
* Steam achievements, leaderboards, multiplayer, cloud saving and trading
  cards
* Secret levels that will test your skills to the max

Install:
~~~~~~~

Unrar, mount/burn, install the game, copy crack, and play

Note:
~~~~~

This is a co-op game only, but local co-op works in our release!
